    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the bread is toasting, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Top, tail and chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1805.-step-3-x200.jpg",
