            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, drain your <strong>jumbo king prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>sliced courgette</strong>, <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> and <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>flakes</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 3 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1805.-step-4-x200.jpg",
